class Form extends React.Component{
    render() {(
        <form className="text-base h-8">
            <label className="text-lg h-8">
                Url:
                <input
                    type="text"
                    name="url"
                    className="h-5 border-2 mx-2 border-black h-8 w-3/6 rounded-lg"
                />
            </label>
            <input type="submit" value="Submit" className="bg-slate-300 p-1 rounded-lg" />
        </form >
    )}
}

export default Form
